</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The rising sun illuminates the Togetsukyo bridge and the red torii gate of Ichitani-Munakata shrine. 昇る太陽が、渡月橋と櫟谷宗像神社の赤い鳥居を照らし出している。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2605_A7R01834-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2605_A7R01834-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Arashiyama Dusk・夕暮れ嵐山</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260524/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Arashiyama Dusk・夕暮れ嵐山" /><published>2026-05-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-05-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama-dusk</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260524/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
